{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "公主连结Re:Dive 新朋友与异世界美食第2话 希望魔盒之龙",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "三人在记忆洞窟遇到了\\n少女模样的龙——光明潘多拉。\\n她为了从名为“影”的怪物手里\\n保护世界而召唤出了佩可莉姆。\\n三人了解情况后决定帮助龙。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "记忆洞窟",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110371_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佩可莉姆",
            "context": "这里就是魔力源点啊～\\n那个女孩提到的地方\\n就是这里了吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20424_03_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_18"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "应该是的……\\n但不知道“记忆聚集的地方”\\n是否真的就是魔力源点……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20424_03_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110296_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "三叶",
            "context": "魔兽的吼叫声！？\\n是从洞窟深处传来的！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20424_03_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110296_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "三叶",
            "context": "库菈乌！佩可莉姆！\\n你们看那个！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20424_03_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210142_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "即使命丧于此，\\n我也不会让你前进半步！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20424_03_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110371_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佩可莉姆",
            "context": "有个女孩正在被魔兽袭击！\\n我们快去救她吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20424_03_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110371_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "3人",
            "context": "哈啊啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20424_03_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_18"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "魔兽变成了……\\n其它魔兽的样子！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20424_03_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110371_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佩可莉姆",
            "context": "不管变成什么样，\\n我们要做的事都一样！\\n火力全开，公主突袭！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20424_03_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110296_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "三叶",
            "context": "这次又变成黑色的雾霭，\\n消失了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20424_03_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110371_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佩可莉姆",
            "context": "那边的人，你没事吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20424_03_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210142_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "谢谢……\\n原来你赶过来了啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20424_03_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110371_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佩可莉姆",
            "context": "这声音……难道你就是\\n那个和我说话的……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20424_03_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210142_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "光明潘多拉",
            "context": "是的……我是光明潘多拉，\\n是把你唤来这里的龙。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20424_03_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210142_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "光明潘多拉",
            "context": "我和双胞胎姐姐\\n在用精神魔法联络的同时，\\n各自在这个世界旅行。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20424_03_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210142_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "光明潘多拉",
            "context": "姐姐用“灾厄之魔盒”封印坏东西，\\n而我则用“希望之魔盒”传递幸福，\\n让这个世界越来越好。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20424_03_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210142_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "光明潘多拉",
            "context": "但突然有一天，\\n我没法和姐姐取得联系了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20424_03_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210142_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "光明潘多拉",
            "context": "与此同时，本应被姐姐\\n封印在魔盒里的怪物——“影”\\n出现在了这片大陆上。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20424_03_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110371_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佩可莉姆",
            "context": "那个“影”究竟是什么啊？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20424_03_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210142_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "光明潘多拉",
            "context": "那是从异界空间\\n来到这个世界的无形怪物。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20424_03_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210142_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "光明潘多拉",
            "context": "虽然平时都是黑色雾霭，\\n但它能模仿所见之物的形态。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20424_03_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110296_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "三叶",
            "context": "黑色雾霭？难道我们\\n刚才赶跑的魔兽是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20424_03_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210142_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "光明潘多拉",
            "context": "那是“影”变化后的形态。\\n我知道“影”的意图后，\\n就一直保护着这个地方。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20424_03_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210142_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "光明潘多拉",
            "context": "这个洞窟深处有魔力源点……\\n“影”企图夺走\\n沉睡在那里的破灭记忆。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20424_03_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_18"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "模仿破灭记忆的能力……\\n难道！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20424_03_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110371_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佩可莉姆",
            "context": "库菈乌，你有什么头绪了吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20424_03_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_18"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "这个世界曾数次遭受\\n巨大魔兽的袭击，破灭记忆\\n指的就是那时的灾厄记忆。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20424_03_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_18"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "“影”是想读取那份记忆，\\n将其实体化吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20424_03_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210142_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "光明潘多拉",
            "context": "是的。它想变成最适合\\n毁灭这个世界的形态……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20424_03_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110371_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佩可莉姆",
            "context": "原来如此。\\n小光是想让我帮忙\\n守护这个魔力源点啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20424_03_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110371_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佩可莉姆",
            "context": "所以才把我唤来这个世界。\\n不过，为什么是我呢？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20424_03_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210142_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "光明潘多拉",
            "context": "“希望之魔盒”是一个\\n能把我所求之物\\n从异界召唤出来的魔盒。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20424_03_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210142_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "光明潘多拉",
            "context": "我对“希望之魔盒”许了愿，\\n请它将重感情的人\\n带来这个世界……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20424_03_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210142_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "光明潘多拉",
            "context": "因为姐姐说过，\\n那个人能彻底打倒“影”。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20424_03_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110371_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佩可莉姆",
            "context": "重感情的人……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20424_03_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210142_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "光明潘多拉",
            "context": "我本来是打算\\n想听了你的回答后\\n再把你带来这个世界的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20424_03_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210142_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "光明潘多拉",
            "context": "如果你希望的话，\\n我就把你送回原来的世界。\\n不过……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20424_03_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210142_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "光明潘多拉",
            "context": "拜托你了！\\n请助我一臂之力吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20424_03_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110371_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佩可莉姆",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20424_03_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_18"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "这是我们这个世界的问题。\\n我认为佩可莉姆\\n不必勉强自己参与战斗。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20424_03_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110296_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "三叶",
            "context": "“影”由我们来打败，\\n佩可莉姆就回到原来的世界……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20424_03_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110371_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佩可莉姆",
            "context": "库菈乌、三叶……\\n谢谢你们为我着想。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20424_03_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110371_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佩可莉姆",
            "context": "但是，我已经决定了。\\n摸头摸头☆",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20424_03_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210142_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "光明潘多拉",
            "context": "诶？那个，佩可莉姆？\\n为什么要摸我的头……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20424_03_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110371_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佩可莉姆",
            "context": "果然……\\n你在颤抖呢，小光。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20424_03_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210142_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "光明潘多拉",
            "context": "！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20424_03_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110371_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佩可莉姆",
            "context": "第一次听到你的声音时，\\n就能感觉到你很紧张～",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20424_03_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110371_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佩可莉姆",
            "context": "虽然你表现得很沉稳，\\n但内心其实很不安吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20424_03_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210142_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "光明潘多拉",
            "context": "我……没办法和姐姐对话……\\n姐姐封印的“影”也复活了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20424_03_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210142_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "光明潘多拉",
            "context": "我担心姐姐是不是出了什么事……\\n但还是觉得要替姐姐\\n做些什么才行……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20424_03_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110371_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佩可莉姆",
            "context": "你是个很努力的孩子。\\n如果我丢下这么让人心疼的孩子\\n回去了，会被伙伴们讨厌的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20424_03_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110371_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佩可莉姆",
            "context": "所以你就放心吧。\\n直到打倒“影”为止，\\n我都会陪在你身边。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20424_03_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210142_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "光明潘多拉",
            "context": "佩可莉姆！\\n呜……呜……呜哇啊啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20424_03_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210142_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佩可莉姆",
            "context": "好啦好啦♪乖孩子♪",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20424_03_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_18"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "在解决问题之前，\\n请让我们也同行。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20424_03_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110296_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "三叶",
            "context": "毕竟我们不能眼睁睁地\\n放任世界危机和哭泣的龙不管。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20424_03_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110371_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佩可莉姆",
            "context": "好！大家齐心协力，\\n一起打倒“影”吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20424_03_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}